skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my butler
des:
Your virtual home butler which can help you to remember the things which your family member generally keeps. 

It can also welcome your guest based on the weather and the day time

Alexa, tell my butler to keep my wallet in drawer
Alexa, ask my butler where is my wallet
Alexa, tell my butler to welcome John
Alexa, tell my butler to find my wallet
